<emphasis id="281509103B2651273B7912A23DD3E3E3" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis id="78CC2DE5CDCC38B696F62A5BFDC364D0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Head</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
Frons and vertex with interspaces between punctures 1-3 
<normalizedToken id="DC06C9E3B85DBF36416FE6D2E3644221" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
